500__a: European Patent Office Application No: 00114246.2 NOVELTY - A packet processing unit is selected among several packet processing units (PPU 11-PPU M) in response to entry of a data packet at an input port (114) of a router (110). A request is forwarded to the selected packet processing unit for acquiring information about the output port to which the packet is to be forwarded. USE - For processing data packets in switched communication network. ADVANTAGE - Resource utilization is optimized resulting in higher packet processing speed and lower power requirements.
